name: Lost
description: Life is weird, isn’t it? It’s full of ups and downs, one day you can be on top of the world, the next one back to the bottom where you came from. You constantly encounter heartbreak, euphoria, disappointment, pride and everything in between. Most of the time you might feel lost and wondering what the hell are you actually doing, what’s the end game here. Maybe one day you’ll find your purpose or maybe you won’t, who knows…
